t: "ЖҒen jokkayЙ“e NulaaЙ—o on, Annabaajo humammbinneejo, on mo Й“e tawta fii mun no winndaa ka maЙ“Й“e ka Tawreeta e ka Linnjiila. Himo yamira Й“e moЖҙЖҙere, o haЙ—a Й“e ЕӢiГұere, himo daginana Й“e dagiiЙ—i Й—in, o harminana Й“e soЙ“uЙ—i Й—in, o ittana Й“e teddeelo e kolommbooje=tonngi wonunooЙ—e e hoore-maЙ“Й“e. ЖҒen gomЙ—imЙ“e mo, Й“e teddini mo, Й“e walli mo, Й“e jokki annoora JippinaaЙ—o wonndude e makko ; Й“en, ko kamЙ“e woni malaaЙ“e Й“en"